#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn24.12:0.3"
msgid "12. Anantavāsutta "
msgstr "12. The World Is Infinite "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.215, sc1
msgctxt "sn24.12:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn24.12:1.2"
msgid "“Kismiṃ nu kho, bhikkhave, sati, kiṃ upādāya, kiṃ abhinivissa evaṃ diṭṭhi uppajjati: "
msgstr "“Mendicants, when what exists, because of grasping what and insisting on what, does the view arise: "

msgctxt "sn24.12:1.3"
msgid "‘anantavā loko’”ti? "
msgstr "‘The world is infinite’?” … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn24.12:1.4"
msgid "“Bhagavaṃmūlakā no, bhante, dhammā … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn24.12:1.5"
msgid "niyato sambodhiparāyano”ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn24.12:1.6"
msgid "Dvādasamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

